@qingyuanxingsi Your error message usually means you don't export the GPU code correctly.
I am not familiar with cpp deployment. But I think "*.o" only works for cpu backend. You should use
`lib.export_library`  (not `lib.save`) to export the library for gpu.

@kevinthesun 

Do you plan to support OpenCL for mobilenet ssd?

Thanks,
